GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF NORTH CAROLINA
SESSION 2025
S 1
SENATE BILL 740
Short Title: Funds for Council for Children's Rights. (Public)
Sponsors: Senator Mohammed (Primary Sponsor).
Referred to: Rules and Operations of the Senate
March 26, 2025
1 A BILL TO BE ENTITLED
2 AN ACT TO APPROPRIATE FUNDS TO FOR THE COUNCIL FOR CHILDREN'S RIGHTS.
3 The General Assembly of North Carolina enacts:
4 SECTION 1. There is appropriated from the General Fund to the Office of State
5 Budget and Management the sum of two hundred fifty thousand dollars ($250,000) in
6 non-recurring funds for the 2025-2026 fiscal year to provide a directed grant to the Council for
7 Children's Rights, Inc. for operating expenses.
8 SECTION 2. This act becomes effective July 1, 2025.
*S740-v-1*

